<div class="contactheading">
  <h2><strong>How our ratings work</strong></h2>
</div>

<div class="hit-container col-sm-12">
  <div class="help col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1">
    <p>Once you have clicked on a property to view, we have provided some important and useful information to help you make a better choice. Click on each individual tab which is named
    according to the type of information that we are displaying to you. Once you have looked at
    each tab, go back to the property information and look at whether we see it as a positive or
    negative opportunity.</p><p>Through the use of a five point rating, we have scored and indicated
    whether we believe a property to be an above average, average or below average opportunity. This is based on price, crime rating to calculate an overall score for opportunity. For
    your convenience and for an easier understanding, we have used three colours alongside each rating.</p>
  </div>
